" Wrap current word
vnoremap <leader>' lb<esc>i'<esc>ea'<esc>v
vnoremap <leader>) lb<esc>i(<esc>ea)<esc>v
vnoremap <leader>( lb<esc>i(<esc>ea)<esc>v
vnoremap <leader>] lb<esc>i[<esc>ea]<esc>v
vnoremap <leader>[ lb<esc>i[<esc>ea]<esc>v
vnoremap <leader>} lb<esc>i{<esc>ea}<esc>v
vnoremap <leader>{ lb<esc>i{<esc>ea}<esc>v

" Wrap current line
vnoremap <leader>'' l0<esc>i'<esc>ea'<esc>v
vnoremap <leader>)) l0<esc>i(<esc>A)<esc>v
vnoremap <leader>(( l0<esc>i(<esc>A)<esc>v
vnoremap <leader>]] l0<esc>i[<esc>A]<esc>v
vnoremap <leader>[[ l0<esc>i[<esc>A]<esc>v
vnoremap <leader>}} l0<esc>i{<esc>A}<esc>v
vnoremap <leader>{{ l0<esc>i{<esc>A}<esc>v

"tab text while in visual mode
vnoremap <Tab> >


